{"title":"Mondraker Kids Get Rad on Scaled-Down Performance Mountain Bikes & eBikes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-kids-get-rad-on-scaled-down-performance-mountain-bikes-ebikes/","date":1701713376000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, shredding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_shredding-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Mondraker’s new Kids MTB lineup includes 2 full-suspension platforms and hardtails in 4 wheelsizes to kit out the next generation of mountain bikers on inspirational rides. The progressive Spanish mountain bike maker wants families to ride together, and keep riding together. So, Mondraker put together a comprehensive Kids mountain bike range that goes from starter bikes with 16″ wheels all the way up to 26″ full-suspension trail bikes you’d be hard-pressed to pick-out from their modern adult mountain bikes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of that, Mondraker sneaks in two Play-series hardtail or full-suspension lightweight ebikes to give young riders the little extra boost they need to join fit parents for longer rides. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2024 Mondraker Kids wide mountain bike range</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, ridge riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Mondraker)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Mondraker says they take kids bikes “very seriously”. So, they aimed to give kids adult-level performance and all their latest tech advancements. Bikes that look, feel &amp; ride just like their adult bikes out on the trail with the fam.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The latest evolution of their Zero Suspension setup and progressive Forward Geometry. Proper 2.4″ tires and dropper post compatibility across the range. Plus, the literal same materials with which they build their popular alloy Foxy and Raze mountain bikes for adults. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_riding-downhill-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And topping it all off, suspension with lighter kid-specific shock tunes and build kits that focus on performance &amp; lightweight, at pricepoints that shouldn’t break your parent’s bank.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Trick hardtails with 16”, 20”, 24”, or 26” wheels</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, Trick 16\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-16-singlespeed-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Trick 16</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Your first mountain bike probably was and your kid’s first mountain bike probably should be a hardtail. The new Mondraker Trick is a no-nonsense mountain bike for all ages with options for 16”, 20”, 24”, or 26” wheels. For such a simple bike, it’s a big step up from their old Leader. And looks a lot more like a proper modern Mondraker adult hardtail.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, Trick 20\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-20in-rigid-hardtail-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Trick 20</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All are built with light Alloy Stealth Evo 6061 aluminum. And get proper modern details like sensible internal cable routing, 12x142mm hub spacing, and a UDH mech hanger. (The 16″ is a single-speed with horizontal track ends dropouts.) And proper 2.4″ tires, even if they aren’t tubeless ready out of the box. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, Trick 24\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-24-alloy-hardtail-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Trick 24</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Each comes in one frame size per wheelsize. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, Trick 26\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_Trick-26-hardtail-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Trick 26</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Trick 16 sells for $750 / 600€. Trick 20 for $950 / 750€. The Trick 24 for $1550 / 1200€. And Trick 26 for $1750 / 1400€.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>F-Trick full-suspension trail bikes with 24” or 26” wheels</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, riding downhill\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_descending-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>At the top level Mondraker has scaled-down their 6061 alloy 130mm Raze trail bike to build a full-suspension mountain bike to give kids proper adult level performance. First, off the list, the all-new F-Trick gets Forward Geometry tweaked for smaller riders. Then, the same recently updated Zero Suspension System with more progressive kinematics as the XC F-Podium &amp; all-mountain Neat. That update alone brings improved initial small bump sensitivity and better compliance out on the trail in a lighter, more compact system with less unsprung weight.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, F-Trick 24\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-24-trail-fully-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker F-Trick 24</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And it adds more travel than ever for a Mondraker Kids full-suspension bike. With 24″ wheels kids get 120mm of travel front &amp; rear. Or on 26″ wheels that scales up to 130mm of rear wheel travel paired to a 140mm fork.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the details, both bikes get proper Boost 12x148mm thru-axles, a UDH, a BSA BB, short 30mm stems, powerful disc brakes (2-piston for the 24″ &amp; 4-piston for the 26″), and dropper posts.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new progressive youth mountain bikes, F-Trick 26\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Mondraker-Kids-all-new-progressive-youth-mountain-bikes_F-Trick-26-full-suspension-trail-bike-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker F-Trick 26</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Again each comes in one frame size per wheelsize. The F-Trick 24 sells for $2600 / 2300€. And the F-Trick 26 for $2800 / 2500€.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Mondraker Kids eBikes too!</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Matching up each of the two regular kids mountain bike lines are a couple of matching Play-series light ebike variants. These are developed to offer just a little bit of support to extend how far your kids can ride and how much cumulative climbing they can do in a ride with a bit of pedal assist. The Play &amp; F-Play both feature Mahle’s lightweight 40Nm ebikemotion X35 hub motor out back and small 250Wh batteries tucked inside their alloy downtubes. Plus, the option for a 210Wh range extender exclusively on the 26″ hardtail &amp; 26″ full-suspension ebikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, internal battery detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-ebike-frame-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The intention was more to create a light &amp; smooth pedal-assist that retained a natural ride feel for young mountain bikers. But it also resulted in the Play &amp; F-Play being almost indiscernible from the Trick &amp; F-Trick unless you look really close.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Play ebike hardtails with 20”, 24”, or 26” wheels</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, Play 20\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-20-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Play 20 ebike</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like the Trick, the Play ebike comes in lots of wheelsizes to fit many young riders. Pretty much the only difference for the ebike hardtails is a slightly larger downtube that drops a bit steeper to finish in front of the threaded BB shell, with a built-in molded rubber bashguard over the battery access. The result is a good low weight and balance front to rear.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, Play 24\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-24-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Play 24 ebike</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, light Alloy Stealth Evo 6061 aluminum frames &amp; Forward Geometry. Proper 2.4″ tires, internal cables &amp; dropper compatibility. But classic QR dropouts to work with the 9mm bolt-on axle of the X35 hub motor. (The 20″ model gets reduced power and a reduced top speed to keep smaller riders safely in check.)</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, Play 26\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_Play-26-hardtail-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker Play 26 ebike</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Each again comes in one frame size per wheelsize. The Play 20 sells for $3000 / 2400€. Play 24 for $3200 / 2800€. And the Play 26 for $3400 / 2900€.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>F-Play full-suspension trail ebikes with 24” or 26” wheels</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, jumping\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-light-full-suspension-ebike-jumping-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Then at the top of the Mondraker Kids ebike family is the full-suspension F-Play. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, brothers riding together\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_brothers-riding-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They say, “<em>If you want your little-ones to get better at mountain biking you’ll need a </em>[e]<em>bike that helps them do just that. That’s why we’ve completely redesigned our F-Play range, making them unarguably the best two-wheeled investment ever when it comes to smiles per mile. We’ve gone all-in, leveraging adult-</em>[e]<em>bike tech to design the best kids </em>[e]<em>bikes out there.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, F-Play 24\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-24-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker F-Play 24 ebike</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s pretty much exactly like the hardtail solution, carbon copy the F-Trick but give it a Mahle X35 motor and a 250Wh battery inside a forward downtube to create the F-Play. It’s the same 24″ wheels with 120/120mm travel or 26″ wheels with 140/130mm travel front &amp; rear. Lightweight, light and natural pedal assist, plus the latest kinematics upgrades and modern Forward Geometry. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, F-Play 26\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_F-Play-26-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>2024 Mondraker F-Play 26 ebike</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 6061 alloy F-Play ebike also comes in one frame size per wheelsize. The F-Play 24 sells for $3700 / 3300€. And the F-Play 26 for $4000 / 3500€. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time.jpg\" alt=\"2024 Mondraker Kids all-new Mahle X35 lightweight mountain ebikes, family riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/2024-Mondraker-Kids-mountain-ebikes_family-trail-time-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>According to Mondraker, “<em>The time has come for your whole family to form a part of the Mondraker family</em>.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://mondraker.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Mondraker.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mondraker-kids-get-rad-on-scaled-down-performance-mountain-bikes-ebikes/\">Mondraker Kids Get Rad on Scaled-Down Performance Mountain Bikes &amp; eBikes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f8b45f60bc925248918f29929a6ea9413909a73b2ba4ba457309cf3929f717a8","category":"Cycling"}